title: MUMBLE_SET_VOLUME_OVERRIDE
content:
0x61C309E3// MumbleSetVolumeOverride
void MUMBLE_SET_VOLUME_OVERRIDE(Player player, float volume);Parameters:player: A game player index.volume: The volume, ranging from 0.0 to 1.0 (or above).Overrides the output volume for a particular player on Mumble. This will also bypass 3D audio and distance calculations. -1.0 to reset the override.Set to -1.0 to reset the Volume override.
